cp|8|AT|
^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|I play any suit which you would overcall at the 2 level can be treated as a single suit. certainly a 5-card suit with 2 of the top 3 honors qualifies. But, I would say most people feel you should have a six card suit.|
